title: Starts of the Week + Week 10 Breakdown, Never Not Working - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/11
description:
It’s football time! Week 10 is here and The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason dive into Week 10 matchups and reveal their Starts of the Week! Plus, injury updates, and a new edition of “Never Not Working!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 11th, 2021.
  
 (04:25) - Never Not Working
 (12:20) - NFL News
 (23:25) - Fantasy Forecast
 (24:10) - Falcons at Cowboys
 (31:40) - Saints at Titans
 (37:40) - Jaguars at Colts
 (42:55) - Browns at Patriots
 (48:35) - Bills at Jets
 (55:15) - Lions at Steelers
 (01:00:20) - Starts of the Week
 (01:00:30) - QB Starts of the Week 
 (01:01:50) - RB Starts of the Week 
 (01:04:55) - WR Starts of the Week
 (01:00:00) - TE Starts of the Week
 (01:10:00) - Boom Boom Kicker of the Week
